<L>__{interior department store day}
<A>__{jeremy is at the department store in the first aid section, picking out some gauze and disinfectant. when he looks down the aisle and sees sam, he moves toward her quickly... he disturbs her while she's looking at some feminine hygiene}
<B>__{products.}
